sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as User (Patient/Parent/Couple)
    participant UI as Nfs Interface (Dashboard)
    participant Engine as AI Recommendation Engine
    participant DB as Specialists & Groups DB

    User->>UI: Select Category (Individual / Child / Couple / Family / Group)
    UI->>Engine: Request Targeted Questions for Category
    Engine-->>UI: Return Questions (Anxiety, Burnout, Roles, etc.)
    
    Note over User,UI: User answers based on Scores (10, 8, 7, 5)
    
    User->>UI: Submit Assessment
    UI->>Engine: Process Answers (Calculate Total & Section Scores)
    
    activate Engine
    
    alt Critical Red Flag (Score >= 50)
        Engine-->>UI: Immediate Alert: Redirect to Psychiatrist / Emergency
        Note right of Engine: Case: Self-harm, Abuse, or Violence
    
    else Specialized Path (Section Score > 15)
        Engine->>DB: Fetch Specialized Professionals (e.g., CBT, Marriage Therapist)
        DB-->>Engine: List of Specialists
        Engine-->>UI: Recommend Specialized Therapist (e.g., Child Psychologist)
        
        opt For Groups Category
            Engine->>DB: Match with Specific Room (e.g., Workplace Circle)
            DB-->>UI: Suggest Joining "Work Stress" Group Room
        end

    else Mixed Path (Score 10 - 15)
        Engine->>DB: Fetch General Practitioners / Life Coaches
        DB-->>Engine: List of General Counselors
        Engine-->>UI: Recommend General Support / Parenting Consultant
        
    else Low Score / Support Path (Score < 10)
        Engine-->>UI: Suggest "General Lounge" or Wellness Content
        Note right of Engine: Case: Daily challenges or simple venting
    end
    
    deactivate Engine
    UI-->>User: Show Personalized Path & Specialist Contact